                    appropriated for construcing a town resevoir, and committee appointed to select
                    a location. -Engine &amp; House repaired for $80 -Street &amp; Culvert
                    near A. M. Mosley's repaired -S. J. Davis apointed Winder of Town Clock,
                    $25/year -50 cents returned to Shott for incorrect assesment -Expenses, Accounts
                    and salary paid to William Craig, chief of police</summary>
